=== Etymology ===
From Italian

== [[noun]] ==
# an Italian pie consisting of a thinly rolled bread dough crust with a spicy tomato sauce spread over the surface of the dough, sprinkled liberally with cheese and often having other toppings as well. It is baked in an oven and usually served as wedged slices.

